        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/duchamp/" class="name">逍遥兽</a>

            <span class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>

        <span content="2007-07-16" class="main-meta">2007-07-16 11:46:34</span>


            <span class="publisher right">
                <a class="publisher" target="_blank" href="https://book.douban.com/subject/1085883/">花城出版社1997版</a>
